 to\na single Mach reflexion irregular refraction $MRR$ and convex-forwards\nirregular refraction $CFR$ that occur in the hydrodynamic case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Nov 2021 18:19:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
