r improvement is due to asking a qualitatively different question, and our\nresults open doors to the study of quantum algorithms in the average case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Nov 2021 18:49:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 2 Apr 2023 23:23:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-04"}
