es\nand challenges are discussed. TULIPS is open source and free. Aside from being\na research tool, it can be used for preparing teaching and public outreach\nmaterial.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Nov 2021 19:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-11"}
