rations and\noffline data for robotic manipulation.Please see https://awopt.github.io for\nmore details.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Nov 2021 21:27:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Nov 2021 16:41:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-12"}
