 simulations are postprocessed and\ncompared to experimental data. Results show agreement between experimental data\nand N-body simulations using the fragmentation rates determined by molecular\ndynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Nov 2021 23:28:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-17"}
